<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n11020g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n11" href="#n11020g">N11 (VI.B.5)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n11all.htm#n11020g"> 20(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> declining years</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">ST. JOSEPH&apos;S ASYLUM / PORTLAND ROW. / A SERMON / WILL BE PREACHED ON / SUNDAY NEXT, MAY 25th / In the / CHURCH OF ST. FRANCIS / XAVIER, / UPPER GARDINER STREET, / At the 12 o&apos;clock Mass, by / REV. E. LEEN , D.D., C.S.Sp., / In Aid of / ST. JOSEPH&apos;S ASYLUM, PORT-/LAND ROW, / <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> / This being the only Institution in Ireland to which single ladies in their <mark>declining years</mark> can look for a home, where they are devotedly cared for, and wherein to close their devout lives in happiness and peace, within the shadow of the Sanctuary, &ldquo;The Poor Servants of the Mother of God&rdquo; in charge of the Institution, earnestly appeal to the charitable public for help according to their means. <small> <a name="FJ23may24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ23may24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (23 May 1924) 4/2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
